            <Para>It was established that majority seeds of <Emphasis Type="Italic">Ae. hippocastanum</Emphasis> L. taken in area neighboring with Metallurgical Plant in Dneprodzerzhinsk city have got more poor composition of protein (Fig. <InternalRef RefID="Fig00171">17.1</InternalRef>). <Figure Category="Standard" Float="Yes" ID="Fig00171">
